license: Apache-2.0
version: "2.0.0"
date-released: "2025-01-01"
keywords:
  - large-language-model
  - transformer
  - mixture-of-experts
  - multi-head-latent-attention
  - deep-learning
abstract: >-
  APEX-1 is a decoder-only transformer LLM that synthesizes innovations
  from Claude, GPT-4.5, DeepSeek-V3, Qwen3, Gemma 4, GLM-4, KIMI,
  MiniMax, and Llama 3 into one coherent architecture. Features include
  MLA, GQA with sliding window, hierarchical MoE, auxiliary-loss-free
  load balancing, dynamic skip gates, multi-token prediction, and
  built-in chain-of-thought reasoning.
